"ທຸກຄັ້ງທີ່ມີການປ່ຽນແປງການແປຂໍ້ຄວາມຈາກ VCS, ມັນຈະຖືກໝາຍວ່າຕ້ອງໄດ້ຮັບການຂຽນໃໝ່ໃນ Weblate. "
"ມີປະໂຫຍດຫຼາຍຖ້າໄຟລ໌ການແປຖືກປັບປຸງດ້ວຍຕົນເອງ ຫຼື ໂດຍບໍລິການພາຍນອກເລື້ອຍໆ."

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:130
msgid "Path of generated MO file"
msgstr "ເສັ້ນທາງຂອງໄຟລ໌ MO ທີ່ສ້າງຂຶ້ນ"

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:134
msgid "If not specified, the location of the PO file will be used."
msgstr "ຫາກບໍ່ໄດ້ລະບຸ, ຈະໃຊ້ສະຖານທີ່ດຽວກັບໄຟລ໌ PO."

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:138
msgid "Include strings needing editing"
msgstr "ລວມຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ຕ້ອງໄດ້ຮັບການແກ້ໄຂ"

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:141
msgid ""
"Strings needing editing (fuzzy) are typically not ready for use as "
"translations."
msgstr "ຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ຕ້ອງໄດ້ຮັບການແກ້ໄຂ (fuzzy) ປົກກະຕິແລ້ວແມ່ນຍັງບໍ່ພ້ອມທີ່ຈະໃຊ້ເປັນການແປ."

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:167
msgid "Update frequency"
msgstr "ຄວາມຖີ່ໃນການປັບປຸງ"

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:169
msgid "Daily"
msgstr "ລາຍວັນ"

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:170
msgid "Weekly"
msgstr "ລາຍອາທິດ"

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:171
msgid "Monthly"
msgstr "ລາຍເດືອນ"

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:176
msgid ""
"How often the add-on should update the POT file when the component is "
"refreshed."
msgstr "ຄວາມຖີ່ທີ່ສ່ວນເສີມຄວນປັບປຸງໄຟລ໌ POT ເມື່ອສ່ວນປະກອບຖືກຣີເຟຣຊ (refresh)."

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:180
msgid "Normalize POT header"
msgstr "ປັບສ່ວນຫົວ (header) ຂອງ POT ໃຫ້ເປັນມາດຕະຖານ"

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:184
msgid "Updates gettext headers and replaces placeholder POT comments."
msgstr "ປັບປຸງສ່ວນຫົວຂອງ gettext ແລະ ແທນທີ່ຄວາມຄິດເຫັນ POT ທີ່ເປັນຕົວແທນ."

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:188
msgid "Update PO files using msgmerge"
msgstr "ປັບປຸງໄຟລ໌ PO ໂດຍໃຊ້ msgmerge"

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:193
msgid ""
"Ensures the msgmerge add-on is installed and triggers it after the POT file "
"is updated."
msgstr "ຮັບປະກັນວ່າໄດ້ຕິດຕັ້ງສ່ວນເສີມ msgmerge ແລ້ວ ແລະ ກະຕຸ້ນມັນຫຼັງຈາກໄຟລ໌ POT ຖືກປັບປຸງ."

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:197
msgid "Source locations"
msgstr "ສະຖານທີ່ຕົ້ນສະບັບ"

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:199
msgid "Use file format settings"
msgstr "ໃຊ້ການຕັ້ງຄ່າຮູບແບບໄຟລ໌"

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:200
msgid "Extract locations to the POT file"
msgstr "ສະກັດສະຖານທີ່ເຂົ້າໃນໄຟລ໌ POT"

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:201
msgid "Do not extract locations"
msgstr "ບໍ່ຕ້ອງສະກັດສະຖານທີ່"

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:206
msgid ""
"Choose how extraction writes source locations to the POT file. Use this to "
"keep locations in the template while omitting them from translated PO files."
msgstr ""
"ເລືອກວິທີທີ່ການສະກັດຈະຂຽນສະຖານທີ່ຕົ້ນສະບັບລົງໃນໄຟລ໌ POT. ໃຊ້ສິ່ງນີ້ເພື່ອຮັກສາສະຖານທີ່ໄວ້ໃນແມ່ແບບ "
"ແຕ່ບໍ່ໃຫ້ມີໃນໄຟລ໌ PO ທີ່ແປແລ້ວ."

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:251
msgid "Do not extract comments"
msgstr "ບໍ່ຕ້ອງສະກັດຄວາມຄິດເຫັນ"

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:252
msgid "Extract all comments"
msgstr "ສະກັດຄວາມຄິດເຫັນທັງໝົດ"

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:253
msgid "Extract comments with tag"
msgstr "ສະກັດຄວາມຄິດເຫັນທີ່ມີແທັກ (tag)"

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:262
msgid "Code comments"
msgstr "ຄວາມຄິດເຫັນໃນໂຄ້ດ"

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:267
msgid ""
"Choose whether xgettext should extract no comments, all comments, or only "
"comments marked with a specific tag."
msgstr ""
"ເລືອກວ່າ xgettext ບໍ່ຄວນສະກັດຄວາມຄິດເຫັນເລີຍ, ສະກັດທັງໝົດ ຫຼື "
"ສະກັດສະເພາະຄວາມຄິດເຫັນທີ່ມີແທັກທີ່ກຳນົດໄວ້."

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:272
msgid "Comment tag"
msgstr "ແທັກຄວາມຄິດເຫັນ"

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:275
msgid ""
"Tag passed to xgettext for comment extraction when using tagged comment mode."
msgstr "ແທັກທີ່ສົ່ງໄປຫາ xgettext ສຳລັບການສະກັດຄວາມຄິດເຫັນ ເມື່ອໃຊ້ໂໝດຄວາມຄິດເຫັນແບບມີແທັກ."

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:280
msgid "xgettext checks"
msgstr "ການກວດສອບ xgettext"

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:285
msgid "Additional xgettext validation checks to enable for extracted messages."
msgstr "ການກວດສອບຄວາມຖືກຕ້ອງເພີ່ມເຕີມຂອງ xgettext ທີ່ຈະເປີດໃຊ້ງານສຳລັບຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ສະກັດມາ."

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:289
msgid "Additional keyword"
msgstr "ຄຳສຳຄັນເພີ່ມເຕີມ"

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:292
msgid "Optional extra keyword passed to xgettext using --keyword."
msgstr "ຄຳສຳຄັນເພີ່ມເຕີມທີ່ເລືອກໄດ້ ທີ່ສົ່ງໄປຫາ xgettext ໂດຍໃຊ້ --keyword."

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:296
msgid "Use keywords exclusively"
msgstr ""

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:299
msgid ""
"When enabled, passes --keyword without a value to xgettext before the "
"additional keyword, disabling all default keywords so that only the keyword "
"specified above is recognized."
msgstr ""

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:318 weblate/addons/forms.py:422
#: weblate/addons/forms.py:429
msgid "This field is required."
msgstr "ຊ່ອງຂໍ້ມູນນີ້ແມ່ນຈຳເປັນ."

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:328
msgid "An additional keyword is required when using keywords exclusively."
msgstr ""

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:338
msgid "Input source"
msgstr "ແຫຼ່ງຂໍ້ມູນຂາເຂົ້າ"

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:340 weblate/addons/forms.py:360
msgid "Source file patterns"
msgstr "ຮູບແບບໄຟລ໌ຕົ້ນສະບັບ"

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:341
msgid "POTFILES manifest"
msgstr "ໄຟລ໌ລາຍການ POTFILES"

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:346
msgid ""
"Choose whether xgettext should read source files from glob patterns or from "
"a POTFILES/POTFILES.in manifest."
msgstr ""
"ເລືອກວ່າ xgettext ຄວນອ່ານໄຟລ໌ຕົ້ນສະບັບຈາກຮູບແບບ glob ຫຼື ຈາກລາຍການ POTFILES/"
"POTFILES.in."

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:351
msgid "xgettext language"
msgstr "ພາສາ xgettext"

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:355
msgid ""
"Programming language passed to xgettext, for example Python or C. Leave "
"blank to let xgettext guess the language from file extensions."
msgstr ""
"ພາສາໂປຣແກຣມທີ່ສົ່ງໄປຫາ xgettext, ເຊັ່ນ Python ຫຼື C. ປະວ່າງໄວ້ເພື່ອໃຫ້ xgettext "
"ຄາດເດົາພາສາຈາກນາມສະກຸນໄຟລ໌."

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:364
msgid ""
"Newline-separated repository-relative glob patterns for files to extract "
"with xgettext."
msgstr ""
"ຮູບແບບ glob ຂອງໄຟລ໌ທີ່ຈະສະກັດດ້ວຍ xgettext ໂດຍອ້າງອີງຕາມບ່ອນເກັບຂໍ້ມູນ, ແຍກດ້ວຍການຂຶ້ນແຖວໃໝ່."

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:369
msgid "POTFILES path"
msgstr "ເສັ້ນທາງ POTFILES"

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:373
msgid ""
"Repository-relative path to POTFILES or POTFILES.in. Entries are resolved "
"relative to the repository root. If present next to the manifest, "
"POTFILES.skip excludes listed files from extraction."
msgstr ""
"ເສັ້ນທາງທີ່ອ້າງອີງຕາມບ່ອນເກັບຂໍ້ມູນໄປຫາ POTFILES ຫຼື POTFILES.in. "
"ລາຍການຕ່າງໆຈະຖືກອ້າງອີງຈາກຮາກ (root) ຂອງບ່ອນເກັບຂໍ້ມູນ. ຖ້າມີໄຟລ໌ POTFILES.skip "
"ຢູ່ຂ້າງລາຍການ, ໄຟລ໌ທີ່ລະບຸໃນນັ້ນຈະບໍ່ຖືກສະກັດ."

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:439 weblate/trans/models/component.py:6448
msgid "Invalid symbolic link in a repository."
msgstr "ລິ້ງສັນຍະລັກໃນຄັງເກັບບໍ່ຖືກຕ້ອງ."

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:450
msgid "POTFILES path has to point to a file."
msgstr "ເສັ້ນທາງ POTFILES ຕ້ອງຊີ້ໄປຫາໄຟລ໌."

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:459
msgid "Meson preset"
msgstr "ຄ່າຕັ້ງລ່ວງໜ້າ Meson"

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:460
msgid "GLib"
msgstr "GLib"

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:464
msgid ""
"Built-in xgettext argument preset matching Meson gettext integration. The "
"GLib preset adds the keyword and format-flag options used by Meson's gettext "
"helper."
msgstr ""
"ຊຸດການຕັ້ງຄ່າ xgettext ທີ່ຕິດຕົ້າມາ ເຊິ່ງກົງກັບການເຮັດວຽກຂອງ Meson gettext. ຊຸດ GLib "
"ຈະເພີ່ມຄຳສຳຄັນ ແລະ ຕົວເລືອກ format-flag ທີ່ໃຊ້ໂດຍຕົວຊ່ວຍ gettext ຂອງ Meson."

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:496
msgid ""
"The Meson add-on expects a Meson gettext directory with meson.build and "
"POTFILES or POTFILES.in."
msgstr ""
"ສ່ວນເສີມ Meson ຕ້ອງການໄດເລັກທໍຣີ Meson gettext ທີ່ມີ meson.build ແລະ POTFILES ຫຼື "
"POTFILES.in."

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:514
msgid "The component has to define a gettext template for new translations."
msgstr "ສ່ວນປະກອບຕ້ອງກຳນົດແມ່ແບບ gettext ສຳລັບການແປໃໝ່."

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:522
msgid ""
"The Django add-on expects the template for new translations to be named "
"\"django.pot\", \"djangojs.pot\", \"django.po\", or \"djangojs.po\"."
msgstr ""
"ສ່ວນເສີມ Django ຕ້ອງການໃຫ້ແມ່ແບບສຳລັບການແປໃໝ່ມີຊື່ວ່າ \"django.pot\", \"djangojs.pot\", "
"\"django.po\", ຫຼື \"djangojs.po\"."

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:532
msgid "Filtering"
msgstr "ການກັ່ນຕອງ"

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:534
msgctxt "None filtering"
msgid "None"
msgstr "ບໍ່ມີ"

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:535
msgid "Weblate documentation"
msgstr "ເອກະສານຂອງ Weblate"

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:540
msgid ""
"Optionally remove strings that are not useful to translate after Sphinx "
"extraction."
msgstr "ເລືອກລຶບຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ບໍ່ຈຳເປັນໃນການແປຫຼັງຈາກການສະກັດຈາກ Sphinx."

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:564
msgid ""
"The Sphinx add-on expects the template for new translations to be a .pot "
"file."
msgstr "ສ່ວນເສີມ Sphinx ຕ້ອງການໃຫ້ແມ່ແບບສຳລັບການແປໃໝ່ເປັນໄຟລ໌ .pot."

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:575
msgid ""
"The Sphinx add-on expects the template for new translations to live in a "
"\"locales\" directory."
msgstr "ສ່ວນເສີມ Sphinx ຕ້ອງການໃຫ້ແມ່ແບບສຳລັບການແປໃໝ່ຢູ່ໃນໂຟນເດີ \"locales\"."

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:590 weblate/addons/forms.py:596
msgid "Could not determine Sphinx source directory."
msgstr "ບໍ່ສາມາດກຳນົດໂຟນເດີຕົ້ນສະບັບຂອງ Sphinx ໄດ້."

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:605
msgid "Name of generated file"
msgstr "ຊື່ຂອງໄຟລ໌ທີ່ສ້າງຂຶ້ນ"

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:609
msgid "Content of generated file"
msgstr "ເນື້ອໃນຂອງໄຟລ໌ທີ່ສ້າງຂຶ້ນ"

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:647
msgid "Commit squashing"
msgstr "ການຮວມຄອມມິດ"

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:650
msgid "All commits into one"
msgstr "ຮວມທຸກຄອມມິດເປັນອັນດຽວ"

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:651
msgid "Per language"
msgstr "ຕາມພາສາ"

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:652
msgid "Per file"
msgstr "ຕາມໄຟລ໌"

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:653
msgid "Per author"
msgstr "ຕາມຜູ້ຂຽນ"

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:659
msgid "Append trailers to squashed commit message"
msgstr "ເພີ່ມສ່ວນທ້າຍ (trailers) ໃສ່ຂໍ້ຄວາມຄອມມິດທີ່ຖືກຮວມ"

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:663
msgid ""
"Trailer lines are lines that look similar to RFC 822 e-mail headers, at the "
"end of the otherwise free-form part of a commit message, such as 'Co-"
"authored-by: …'."
msgstr ""
"ແຖວສ່ວນທ້າຍແມ່ນແຖວທີ່ມີລັກສະນະຄ້າຍຄືກັບສ່ວນຫົວອີເມວ RFC 822, ຢູ່ຕອນທ້າຍຂອງຂໍ້ຄວາມຄອມມິດ, ເຊັ່ນ "
"'Co-authored-by: …'."

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:669
msgid "Commit message"
msgstr "ຂໍ້ຄວາມຄອມມິດ"

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:673
msgid ""
"This commit message will be used instead of the combined commit messages "
"from the squashed commits."
