msgstr "ເລືອກວ່າເຫດການການປ່ຽນແປງໃດຄວນເປີດການເຮັດວຽກຂອງສ່ວນເສີມນີ້."

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:1647
#: weblate/templates/vcs/github_app_register.html:57
msgid "Webhook URL"
msgstr "URL ເວັບຮຸກ"

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:1667 weblate/vcs/github.py:455
msgid "Webhook secret"
msgstr "ລະຫັດລັບເວັບຮຸກ"

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:1673
msgid "The Standard Webhooks secret is a base64 encoded string."
msgstr "ລະຫັດລັບ Standard Webhooks ແມ່ນຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ເຂົ້າລະຫັດແບບ base64."

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:1687
msgid "AMQP broker URL"
msgstr "URL ຂອງ AMQP broker"

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:1688
msgid "The AMQP broker URL to connect to."
msgstr "URL ຂອງ AMQP broker ທີ່ຈະເຊື່ອມຕໍ່."

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:1692
msgid "Topic prefix"
msgstr "ຄຳນຳໜ້າຫົວຂໍ້ (Topic prefix)"

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:1694
msgid "Optional prefix to prepend to generated message topics."
msgstr "ຄຳນຳໜ້າທີ່ຈະຕື່ມໃສ່ຫົວຂໍ້ຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ສ້າງຂຶ້ນ (ເລືອກໄດ້)."

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:1700
msgid "CA certificate bundle (PEM)"
msgstr "ຊຸດໃບຢັ້ງຢືນ CA (PEM)"

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:1702
msgid ""
"Paste only PEM certificate blocks, each starting with \"-----BEGIN "
"CERTIFICATE-----\" and ending with \"-----END CERTIFICATE-----\"."
msgstr ""
"ວາງສະເພາະບລັອກໃບຢັ້ງຢືນ PEM, ແຕ່ລະບລັອກຕ້ອງຂຶ້ນຕົ້ນດ້ວຍ \"-----BEGIN CERTIFICATE-----\" "
"ແລະ ລົງທ້າຍດ້ວຍ \"-----END CERTIFICATE-----\"."

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:1708
msgid "Client private key (PEM)"
msgstr "ຄີສ່ວນຕົວຂອງໄຄເອັນ (PEM)"

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:1710
msgid ""
"Paste a single unencrypted PEM private key block. Encrypted private keys are "
"not supported."
msgstr ""
"ວາງບລັອກ PEM private key ທີ່ບໍ່ໄດ້ເຂົ້າລະຫັດພຽງອັນດຽວ. ບໍ່ຮອງຮັບ private key ທີ່ເຂົ້າລະຫັດ."

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:1717
msgid "Client certificate (PEM)"
msgstr "ໃບຢັ້ງຢືນຂອງໄຄເອັນ (PEM)"

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:1719
msgid ""
"Paste only the PEM certificate block starting with \"-----BEGIN "
"CERTIFICATE-----\"; do not paste the output from \"openssl x509 -text\"."
msgstr ""
"ວາງສະເພາະບລັອກໃບຢັ້ງຢືນ PEM ທີ່ຂຶ້ນຕົ້ນດ້ວຍ \"-----BEGIN CERTIFICATE-----\"; "
"ຫ້າມວາງຂໍ້ມູນຈາກ \"openssl x509 -text\"."

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:1724
msgid "Publish timeout"
msgstr "ໝົດເວລາການເຜີຍແຜ່"

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:1726
msgid "How many seconds to wait for the broker delivery acknowledgement."
msgstr "ຈຳນວນວິນາທີທີ່ຈະລໍຖ້າການຕອບຮັບການສົ່ງຈາກ broker."

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:1734
msgid "Connection attempts"
msgstr "ຄວາມພະຍາຍາມໃນການເຊື່ອມຕໍ່"

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:1735
msgid "How many times to try connecting to the broker."
msgstr "ຈຳນວນຮອບທີ່ຈະພະຍາຍາມເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ຫາ broker."

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:1742
msgid "Retry delay"
msgstr "ໄລຍະເວລາລໍຖ້າກ່ອນລອງໃໝ່"

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:1743
msgid "How many seconds to wait between connection attempts."
msgstr "ຈຳນວນວິນາທີທີ່ຈະລໍຖ້າລະຫວ່າງການພະຍາຍາມເຊື່ອມຕໍ່."

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:1792
msgid "Topic prefix can contain only ASCII characters."
msgstr "ຄຳນຳໜ້າຫົວຂໍ້ສາມາດມີໄດ້ສະເພາະຕົວອັກສອນ ASCII ເທົ່ານັ້ນ."

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:1797
#, python-format
msgid "Topic prefix must not exceed %(limit)d characters."
msgstr "ຄຳນຳໜ້າຫົວຂໍ້ຕ້ອງບໍ່ເກີນ %(limit)d ຕົວອັກສອນ."

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:1831
msgid "The SSL certificates have to be provided for SSL connection."
msgstr "ຕ້ອງສະໜອງໃບຢັ້ງຢືນ SSL ສຳລັບການເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ແບບ SSL."

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:1844
msgid "The SSL certificates are not used without a SSL connection."
msgstr "ໃບຢັ້ງຢືນ SSL ຈະບໍ່ຖືກນຳໃຊ້ຫາກບໍ່ມີການເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ແບບ SSL."

#: weblate/addons/generate.py:51
msgid "Statistics generator"
msgstr "ຕົວສ້າງສະຖິຕິ"

#: weblate/addons/generate.py:53
msgid "Generates a file containing detailed info about the translation status."
msgstr "ສ້າງໄຟລ໌ທີ່ມີຂໍ້ມູນລະອຽດກ່ຽວກັບສະຖານະການແປ."

#: weblate/addons/generate.py:192
msgid "Pseudolocale generation"
msgstr "ການສ້າງ Pseudolocale"

#: weblate/addons/generate.py:194
msgid ""
"Generates a translation by adding prefix and suffix to source strings "
"automatically."
msgstr "ສ້າງການແປໂດຍການຕື່ມຄຳນຳໜ້າ ແລະ ຄຳລົງທ້າຍໃສ່ຂໍ້ຄວາມຕົ້ນສະບັບໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດ."

#: weblate/addons/generate.py:281
msgid "Prefill translation with source"
msgstr "ຕື່ມຂໍ້ມູນການແປດ້ວຍຕົ້ນສະບັບໄວ້ກ່ອນ"

#: weblate/addons/generate.py:282
msgid "Fills in translation strings with source string."
msgstr "ຕື່ມຂໍ້ຄວາມການແປດ້ວຍຂໍ້ຄວາມຕົ້ນສະບັບ."

#: weblate/addons/generate.py:320
msgid "Fill read-only strings with source"
msgstr "ຕື່ມຂໍ້ຄວາມແບບອ່ານໄດ້ຢ່າງດຽວດ້ວຍຕົ້ນສະບັບ"

#: weblate/addons/generate.py:322
msgid "Fills in translation of read-only strings with source string."
msgstr "ຕື່ມການແປຂອງຂໍ້ຄວາມແບບອ່ານໄດ້ຢ່າງດຽວດ້ວຍຂໍ້ຄວາມຕົ້ນສະບັບ."

#: weblate/addons/gettext.py:99
msgid "Generate MO files"
msgstr "ສ້າງໄຟລ໌ MO"

#: weblate/addons/gettext.py:101
msgid "Automatically generates a MO file for every changed PO file."
msgstr "ສ້າງໄຟລ໌ MO ໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດສຳລັບທຸກໄຟລ໌ PO ທີ່ມີການປ່ຽນແປງ."

#: weblate/addons/gettext.py:142
msgid "Update LINGUAS file"
msgstr "ອັບເດດໄຟລ໌ LINGUAS"

#: weblate/addons/gettext.py:144
msgid "Updates the LINGUAS file when a translation is added or removed."
msgstr "ອັບເດດໄຟລ໌ LINGUAS ເມື່ອມີການເພີ່ມ ຫຼື ລຶບການແປ."

#: weblate/addons/gettext.py:292
msgid "Update ALL_LINGUAS variable in the \"configure\" file"
msgstr "ອັບເດດຕົວປ່ຽນ ALL_LINGUAS ໃນໄຟລ໌ \"configure\""

#: weblate/addons/gettext.py:294
msgid ""
"Updates the ALL_LINGUAS variable in \"configure\", \"configure.in\" or "
"\"configure.ac\" files, when a translation is added or removed."
msgstr ""
"ອັບເດດຕົວປ່ຽນ ALL_LINGUAS ໃນໄຟລ໌ \"configure\", \"configure.in\" ຫຼື "
"\"configure.ac\" ເມື່ອມີການເພີ່ມ ຫຼື ລຶບການແປ."

#: weblate/addons/gettext.py:400
msgid "Update PO files to match POT (msgmerge)"
msgstr "ອັບເດດໄຟລ໌ PO ໃຫ້ກົງກັບ POT (msgmerge)"

#: weblate/addons/gettext.py:402
msgid ""
"Updates all PO files (as configured by \"File mask\") to match the POT file "
"(as configured by \"Template for new translations\") using msgmerge."
msgstr ""
"ອັບເດດທຸກໄຟລ໌ PO (ຕາມທີ່ຕັ້ງຄ່າໃນ \"File mask\") ໃຫ້ກົງກັບໄຟລ໌ POT (ຕາມທີ່ຕັ້ງຄ່າໃນ "
"\"ແມ່ແບບສຳລັບການແປໃໝ່\") ໂດຍໃຊ້ msgmerge."

#: weblate/addons/gettext.py:1042
msgid "Update POT file (xgettext)"
msgstr "ອັບເດດໄຟລ໌ POT (xgettext)"

#: weblate/addons/gettext.py:1044
msgid "Updates the gettext template using xgettext on selected source files."
msgstr "ອັບເດດແມ່ແບບ gettext ໂດຍໃຊ້ xgettext ໃນໄຟລ໌ຕົ້ນສະບັບທີ່ເລືອກ."

#: weblate/addons/gettext.py:1470
msgid "Update POT file (Meson)"
msgstr "ອັບເດດໄຟລ໌ POT (Meson)"

#: weblate/addons/gettext.py:1472
msgid "Updates the gettext template using Meson gettext conventions."
msgstr "ອັບເດດແມ່ແບບ gettext ໂດຍໃຊ້ຂໍ້ກຳນົດຂອງ Meson gettext."

#: weblate/addons/gettext.py:1626
msgid "Update gettext template (Django)"
msgstr "ອັບເດດແມ່ແບບ gettext (Django)"

#: weblate/addons/gettext.py:1628
msgid ""
"Updates the gettext template using Django's built-in makemessages command."
msgstr "ອັບເດດແມ່ແບບ gettext ໂດຍໃຊ້ຄຳສັ່ງ makemessages ທີ່ມີມາໃນຕົວຂອງ Django."

#: weblate/addons/gettext.py:1820
msgid "Update POT file (Sphinx)"
msgstr "ອັບເດດໄຟລ໌ POT (Sphinx)"

#: weblate/addons/gettext.py:1822
msgid ""
"Updates the gettext template using Sphinx's gettext builder without loading "
"project configuration."
msgstr ""
"ອັບເດດແມ່ແບບ gettext ໂດຍໃຊ້ gettext builder ຂອງ Sphinx ໂດຍບໍ່ຕ້ອງໂຫຼດການຕັ້ງຄ່າໂຄງການ."

#: weblate/addons/gettext.py:2072
msgid "Contributors in comment"
msgstr "ລາຍຊື່ຜູ້ມີສ່ວນຮ່ວມໃນຄຳເຫັນ"

#: weblate/addons/gettext.py:2074
msgid ""
"Updates the comment part of the PO file header to include contributor names "
"and years of contributions."
msgstr "ອັບເດດສ່ວນຄຳເຫັນຂອງສ່ວນຫົວໄຟລ໌ PO ເພື່ອລວມເອົາຊື່ຜູ້ມີສ່ວນຮ່ວມ ແລະ ປີທີ່ໄດ້ປະກອບສ່ວນ."

#: weblate/addons/git.py:45
msgid "Squash Git commits"
msgstr "ຮວມ Git commits"

#: weblate/addons/git.py:46
msgid "Squash Git commits prior to pushing changes."
msgstr "ຮວມ Git commits ກ່ອນທີ່ຈະ push ການປ່ຽນແປງ."

#: weblate/addons/models.py:356 weblate/addons/views.py:433
#: weblate/api/views.py:4646
msgid "This add-on cannot be triggered manually."
msgstr "ສ່ວນເສີມນີ້ບໍ່ສາມາດເປີດເຮັດວຽກດ້ວຍຕົນເອງໄດ້."

#: weblate/addons/properties.py:164
msgid "Format the Java properties file"
msgstr "ຈັດຮູບແບບໄຟລ໌ Java properties"

#: weblate/addons/properties.py:165
msgid "Formats and sorts the Java properties file."
msgstr "ຈັດຮູບແບບ ແລະ ລຽງລຳດັບໄຟລ໌ Java properties."

#: weblate/addons/removal.py:60
msgid "Stale comment removal"
msgstr "ການລຶບຄຳເຫັນທີ່ເກົ່າເກີນໄປ"

#: weblate/addons/removal.py:61
msgid "Set a timeframe for removal of comments."
msgstr "ກຳນົດກອບເວລາສຳລັບການລຶບຄຳເຫັນ."

#: weblate/addons/removal.py:87
msgid "Stale suggestion removal"
msgstr "ການລຶບຄຳແນະນຳທີ່ເກົ່າເກີນໄປ"

#: weblate/addons/removal.py:88
msgid "Set a timeframe for removal of suggestions."
msgstr "ກຳນົດກອບເວລາສຳລັບການລຶບຄຳແນະນຳ."

#: weblate/addons/resx.py:24
msgid "Update RESX files"
msgstr "ອັບເດດໄຟລ໌ RESX"

#: weblate/addons/resx.py:26
msgid ""
"Update all translation files to match the monolingual upstream base file. "
"Unused strings are removed, and new ones added as copies of the source "
"string."
msgstr ""
"ອັບເດດທຸກໄຟລ໌ການແປໃຫ້ກົງກັບໄຟລ໌ພື້ນຖານແບບພາສາເວີຊັນດຽວຈາກຕົ້ນທາງ. ຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ບໍ່ໄດ້ໃຊ້ຈະຖືກລຶບອອກ, "
"ແລະ ຂໍ້ຄວາມໃໝ່ຈະຖືກເພີ່ມໂດຍການຄັດລອກຈາກຂໍ້ຄວາມຕົ້ນສະບັບ."

