msgid "Cloud"
msgstr "ຄລາວ"

#: weblate/templates/accounts/snippets/login-title.html:9
msgctxt "Badge for site title for dedicated instances"
msgid "Dedicated"
msgstr "ແບບສ່ວນຕົວ"

#: weblate/templates/accounts/snippets/login-title.html:11
msgctxt "Badge for site title for self-hosted instances"
msgid "Self-hosted"
msgstr "ຕັ້ງໂຮສເອງ"

#: weblate/templates/accounts/totp.html:27
msgid ""
"Authenticator apps generate time-based one-time passwords that are used as a "
"second factor to verify your identity when prompted during sign-in."
msgstr ""
"ແອັບຢືນຢັນຕົວຕົນຈະສ້າງລະຫັດຜ່ານຄັ້ງດຽວແບບກຳນົດເວລາ (OTP) "
"ເພື່ອໃຊ້ເປັນປັດໄຈທີສອງໃນການຢືນຢັນຕົວຕົນຂອງທ່ານເມື່ອເຂົ້າສູ່ລະບົບ."

#: weblate/templates/accounts/totp.html:30
msgid "Scan the QR code"
msgstr "ສະແກນ QR ໂຄ້ດ"

#: weblate/templates/accounts/totp.html:34
msgid "You can also enter the secret key manually:"
msgstr "ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດປ້ອນຄີລັບດ້ວຍຕົນເອງ:"

