#: weblate/templates/lang/language_edit_warning.html:12
#, python-format
msgid ""
"The language definitions are automatically updated by Weblate upon a "
"database migration. Improper edits will likely get reverted.<a "
"href=\"%(url)s\">Consult the documentation about proper handling of this.</a>"
