#: weblate/templates/snippets/libre-basic.html:10
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Translated content has to be released under a license "
"%(link_osi_start)sapproved by OSI%(link_end)s or "
"%(link_fsf_start)srecognized as libre by FSF%(link_end)s."
msgstr ""
"ເນື້ອຫາທີ່ແປແລ້ວຕ້ອງໄດ້ຮັບການເຜີຍແຜ່ພາຍໃຕ້ໃບອະນຸຍາດທີ່ %(link_osi_start)sໄດ້ຮັບການຮັບຮອງໂດຍ "
"OSI%(link_end)s ຫຼື %(link_fsf_start)sໄດ້ຮັບການຍອມຮັບວ່າເປັນຊອບແວເສລີໂດຍ "
"FSF%(link_end)s."

#: weblate/templates/snippets/libre-basic.html:13
msgid ""
"All the source code has to be libre-licensed and publicly available in a "
"supported version control system."
