msgstr "ລະຫັດພາສາຍ່ອຍທີ່ແນະນຳ"

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/bilingualpoconfiguredasmonolingual.html:3
msgid ""
"The component looks like it contains regular gettext PO files, but it is "
"configured as monolingual gettext PO."
msgstr ""
"ສ່ວນປະກອບນີ້ເບິ່ງຄືວ່າມີໄຟລ໌ gettext PO ແບບປົກກະຕິ, ແຕ່ຖືກກຳນົດຄ່າເປັນ gettext PO ແບບພາສາດຽວ."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/bilingualpoconfiguredasmonolingual.html:4
msgid ""
"If these are bilingual PO files, change the file format to gettext PO file, "
"clear the monolingual base language file, and update the component."
msgstr ""
"ຖ້ານີ້ແມ່ນໄຟລ໌ PO ແບບສອງພາສາ, ໃຫ້ປ່ຽນຮູບແບບໄຟລ໌ເປັນ gettext PO, "
"ລ້າງໄຟລ໌ພາສາພື້ນຖານແບບພາສາດຽວອອກ, ແລ້ວອັບເດດສ່ວນປະກອບ."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/billinglimit.html:4
msgid ""
"Your billing plan has exceeded its limits. You can still use the service, "
"but are recommended to upgrade the billing plan."
msgstr ""
"ແຜນການຊຳລະເງິນຂອງທ່ານເກີນຂີດຈຳກັດແລ້ວ. ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດໃຊ້ບໍລິການໄດ້ຢູ່, "
"ແຕ່ແນະນຳໃຫ້ອັບເກຣດແຜນການຊຳລະເງິນ."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/brokenbrowserurl.html:3
msgid "Weblate could not validate the repository browser URL:"
msgstr "Weblate ບໍ່ສາມາດກວດສອບ URL ຂອງບຣາວເຊີຄັງເກັບຂໍ້ມູນໄດ້:"

#. Translators: This is for the case where the link check fails in Weblate, but the links (shown above this message) work correctly for the user.
#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/brokenbrowserurl.html:14
msgid ""
"In case the above links work for you, they might just require "
"authentication, and it is safe to dismiss this alert."
msgstr ""
"ໃນກໍລະນີທີ່ລິງຂ້າງເທິງໃຊ້ງານໄດ້ສຳລັບທ່ານ, ພວກມັນອາດຈະຕ້ອງການການຢືນຢັນຕົວຕົນ, "
"ທ່ານສາມາດປິດການແຈ້ງເຕືອນນີ້ໄດ້."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/brokenbrowserurl.html:18
msgid ""
"This can happen if the path within the translation files contains references "
"to a parent directory, or is absolute."
msgstr ""
"ສິ່ງນີ້ສາມາດເກີດຂຶ້ນໄດ້ຖ້າເສັ້ນທາງພາຍໃນໄຟລ໌ການແປມີການອ້າງອີງເຖິງໂຟນເດີຫຼັກ ຫຼື ເປັນເສັ້ນທາງແບບເຕັມ "
"(absolute)."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/brokenprojecturl.html:3
msgid "Weblate could not validate the project website URL:"
msgstr "Weblate ບໍ່ສາມາດກວດສອບ URL ເວັບໄຊທ໌ຂອງໂຄງການໄດ້:"

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/cdnaddonerror.html:3
msgid "Weblate CDN add-on could not parse the HTML files."
msgstr "ສ່ວນເສີມ Weblate CDN ບໍ່ສາມາດວິເຄາະໄຟລ໌ HTML ໄດ້."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/cdnaddonerror.html:10
#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/parseerror.html:10
msgid "Filename"
msgstr "ຊື່ໄຟລ໌"

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/common-repo.html:5
msgid ""
"The upstream repository was not found. Please check whether it exists and is "
"accessible to Weblate."
msgstr ""
"ບໍ່ພົບຄັງເກັບຂໍ້ມູນຕົ້ນທາງ. ກະລຸນາກວດສອບວ່າມັນມີຢູ່ແທ້ ຫຼື ບໍ່ ແລະ Weblate ສາມາດເຂົ້າເຖິງໄດ້ ຫຼື ບໍ່."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/common-repo.html:11
msgid ""
"The upstream repository could not be accessed. Please check whether it is "
"accessible to Weblate."
msgstr "ບໍ່ສາມາດເຂົ້າເຖິງຄັງເກັບຂໍ້ມູນຕົ້ນທາງໄດ້. ກະລຸນາກວດສອບວ່າ Weblate ສາມາດເຂົ້າເຖິງໄດ້ ຫຼື ບໍ່."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/common-repo.html:17
msgid ""
"Gerrit prohibited this push. You might need a gerrit-account that has the "
"forge author permissions for the repository/branch or have to use the squash "
"add-on on this component in Weblate."
msgstr ""
"Gerrit ປະຕິເສດການສົ່ງ (push) ນີ້. ທ່ານອາດຈະຕ້ອງໃຊ້ບັນຊີ Gerrit ທີ່ມີສິດ forge author "
"ສຳລັບຄັງເກັບຂໍ້ມູນ/ສາຂານີ້ ຫຼື ຕ້ອງໃຊ້ສ່ວນເສີມ squash ໃນສ່ວນປະກອບນີ້ໃນ Weblate."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/common-repo.html:22
msgid ""
"The upstream repository could not be temporarily accessed. Please try it "
"again later."
msgstr "ບໍ່ສາມາດເຂົ້າເຖິງຄັງເກັບຂໍ້ມູນຕົ້ນທາງໄດ້ຊົ່ວຄາວ. ກະລຸນາລອງໃໝ່ພາຍຫຼັງ."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/common-repo.html:29
msgid ""
"Your repository URL seems to miss credentials. Either provide them in the "
"URL or use SSH with key based authentication."
msgstr ""
"URL ຂອງຄັງເກັບຂໍ້ມູນຂອງທ່ານເບິ່ງຄືວ່າຂາດຂໍ້ມູນການເຂົ້າລະບົບ. ທ່ານສາມາດລະບຸໃນ URL ຫຼື ໃຊ້ SSH "
"ພ້ອມກັບການຢືນຢັນດ້ວຍ key."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/common-repo.html:35
msgid "You might want to use following URL instead:"
msgstr "ທ່ານອາດຈະຕ້ອງການໃຊ້ URL ຕໍ່ໄປນີ້ແທນ:"

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/common-repo.html:41
msgid ""
"You might want to choose Git with force push as version control system in "
"the component configuration to overwrite the remote repository after "
"rebasing commits in Weblate."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານອາດຈະຕ້ອງການເລືອກ Git ແບບບັງຄັບສົ່ງ (force push) "
"ໃນການກຳນົດຄ່າສ່ວນປະກອບເພື່ອຂຽນທັບຄັງເກັບຂໍ້ມູນປາຍທາງຫຼັງຈາກມີການ rebase ຄອມມິດໃນ Weblate."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/common-repo.html:45
msgid ""
"The Weblate repository is missing some commits from upstream. Perhaps it is "
"not receiving notifications upon updates of the remote repository."
msgstr ""
"ຄັງເກັບຂໍ້ມູນ Weblate ຂາດບາງຄອມມິດຈາກຕົ້ນທາງ. "
"ອາດເປັນຍ້ອນມັນບໍ່ໄດ້ຮັບການແຈ້ງເຕືອນເມື່ອມີການອັບເດດໃນຄັງເກັບຂໍ້ມູນປາຍທາງ."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/common-repo.html:50
msgid ""
"Weblate will retry the operation once it is needed again, so the alert might "
"disappear for the temporary issues."
msgstr ""
"Weblate ຈະລອງປະຕິບັດງານໃໝ່ເມື່ອຈຳເປັນ, ດັ່ງນັ້ນການແຈ້ງເຕືອນອາດຈະຫາຍໄປເອງສຳລັບບັນຫາຊົ່ວຄາວ."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/conflictingrepositorysetup.html:4
msgid ""
"Another component is configured to push to the same repository and push "
"branch."
msgstr "ມີສ່ວນປະກອບອື່ນຖືກກຳນົດຄ່າໃຫ້ສົ່ງ (push) ໄປຍັງຄັງເກັບຂໍ້ມູນ ແລະ ສາຂາດຽວກັນ."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/conflictingrepositorysetup.html:5
msgid "This can cause the branch to be overwritten."
msgstr "ສິ່ງນີ້ອາດເຮັດໃຫ້ສາຂາຖືກຂຽນທັບໄດ້."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/conflictingrepositorysetup.html:9
msgid ""
"Use a different push branch for each component, or share the repository "
"using the following Weblate URL:"
msgstr ""
"ໃຫ້ໃຊ້ສາຂາການສົ່ງທີ່ແຕກຕ່າງກັນສຳລັບແຕ່ລະສ່ວນປະກອບ, ຫຼື ແບ່ງປັນຄັງເກັບຂໍ້ມູນໂດຍໃຊ້ URL Weblate "
"ຕໍ່ໄປນີ້:"

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/duplicatefilemask.html:4
msgid ""
"Some linked components have the same file mask or share some of the files."
msgstr "ບາງສ່ວນປະກອບທີ່ເຊື່ອມໂຍງກັນມີການກຳນົດຮູບແບບຊື່ໄຟລ໌ (file mask) ດຽວກັນ ຫຼື ໃຊ້ໄຟລ໌ຮ່ວມກັນ."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/duplicatefilemask.html:5
msgid "Please fix this by removing one of them."
msgstr "ກະລຸນາແກ້ໄຂໂດຍການລຶບອັນໃດອັນໜຶ່ງອອກ."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/duplicatefilemask.html:8
msgid "The following files were found multiple times:"
msgstr "ພົບໄຟລ໌ຕໍ່ໄປນີ້ຫຼາຍຄັ້ງ:"

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/duplicatelanguage.html:5
msgid "The component contains translation file for the source language."
msgstr "ສ່ວນປະກອບນີ້ມີໄຟລ໌ການແປສຳລັບພາສາຕົ້ນສະບັບ."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/duplicatelanguage.html:7
#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/duplicatelanguage.html:35
msgid "Please consider the following:"
msgstr "ກະລຸນາພິຈາລະນາດັ່ງນີ້:"

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/duplicatelanguage.html:12
msgid ""
"You might be using a monolingual translation file as a bilingual one. If "
"that is the case, please set the monolingual base language file location."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານອາດຈະກຳລັງໃຊ້ໄຟລ໌ການແປແບບພາສາດຽວໃນຮູບແບບສອງພາສາ. ຖ້າແມ່ນກໍລະນີນີ້, "
"ກະລຸນາກຳນົດທີ່ຕັ້ງຂອງໄຟລ໌ພາສາພື້ນຖານແບບພາສາດຽວ."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/duplicatelanguage.html:16
msgid ""
"In case translation to the source language is desired, please change the "
"source language in the component settings."
msgstr "ໃນກໍລະນີທີ່ຕ້ອງການແປເປັນພາສາຕົ້ນສະບັບ, ກະລຸນາປ່ຽນພາສາຕົ້ນສະບັບໃນການຕັ້ງຄ່າສ່ວນປະກອບ."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/duplicatelanguage.html:19
msgid ""
"If the translation file for the source language is not needed, please remove "
"it from the repository."
msgstr "ຖ້າບໍ່ຕ້ອງການໄຟລ໌ການແປສຳລັບພາສາຕົ້ນສະບັບ, ກະລຸນາລຶບມັນອອກຈາກຄັງເກັບຂໍ້ມູນ."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/duplicatelanguage.html:22
msgid ""
"If the translation file for the source language is needed, but should be "
"ignored by Weblate, please adjust the language filter to exclude it."
msgstr ""
"ຖ້າຈຳເປັນຕ້ອງມີໄຟລ໌ການແປສຳລັບພາສາຕົ້ນສະບັບ ແຕ່ຕ້ອງການໃຫ້ Weblate ບໍ່ສົນໃຈມັນ, "
"ກະລຸນາປັບຕົວຕອງພາສາເພື່ອຍົກເວັ້ນມັນອອກ."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/duplicatelanguage.html:31
msgid ""
"The component contains several translation files mapped to a single language "
"in Weblate."
msgstr "ສ່ວນປະກອບນີ້ມີໄຟລ໌ການແປຫຼາຍໄຟລ໌ທີ່ຖືກກຳນົດໃຫ້ເປັນພາສາດຽວກັນໃນ Weblate."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/duplicatelanguage.html:32
msgid "Please fix this by removing one of the translation files."
msgstr "ກະລຸນາແກ້ໄຂໂດຍການລຶບໄຟລ໌ການແປອັນໃດອັນໜຶ່ງອອກ."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/duplicatelanguage.html:39
msgid ""
"Avoid having translation files for both the plain language code and its "
"equivalent territory designation (for example de and de_DE)."
msgstr ""
"ຫຼີກລ່ຽງການມີໄຟລ໌ການແປທັງລະຫັດພາສາແບບທຳມະດາ ແລະ ລະຫັດພາສາແບບລະບຸເຂດແດນ (ຕົວຢ່າງ de ແລະ "
"de_DE)."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/duplicatelanguage.html:52
msgid "Language codes"
msgstr "ລະຫັດພາສາ"

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/duplicatelanguage.html:53
msgid "File names"
msgstr "ຊື່ໄຟລ໌"

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/duplicatestring.html:3
msgid "The component contains several duplicated translation strings."
msgstr "ສ່ວນປະກອບນີ້ມີຂໍ້ຄວາມການແປທີ່ຊ້ຳກັນຫຼາຍບ່ອນ."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/duplicatestring.html:12
#: weblate/templates/translate.html:412 weblate/templates/translate.html:515
msgid "Source"
msgstr "ຕົ້ນສະບັບ"

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/duplicatestring.html:33
msgid ""
"Please fix this by removing duplicated strings with same identifier from the "
"translation files."
msgstr "ກະລຸນາແກ້ໄຂໂດຍການລຶບຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ຊ້ຳກັນທີ່ມີລະຫັດລະບຸດຽວກັນອອກຈາກໄຟລ໌ການແປ."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/duplicatestring.html:42
msgid "Remove duplicate strings"
msgstr "ລຶບຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ຊ້ຳກັນ"

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/extractpotmissingmsgmerge.html:3
msgid ""
"This component updates the POT file automatically, but does not update the "
"PO files."
msgstr "ສ່ວນປະກອບນີ້ອັບເດດໄຟລ໌ POT ອັດຕະໂນມັດ, ແຕ່ບໍ່ໄດ້ອັບເດດໄຟລ໌ PO."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/extractpotmissingmsgmerge.html:6
msgid ""
"Install the msgmerge add-on as well if you want translation files to follow "
"template changes automatically."
msgstr ""
"ໃຫ້ຕິດຕັ້ງສ່ວນເສີມ msgmerge ນຳ ຖ້າທ່ານຕ້ອງການໃຫ້ໄຟລ໌ການແປອັບເດດຕາມແມ່ແບບ (template) "
"ອັດຕະໂນມັດ."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/inexacthookmatch.html:4
msgid ""
"The last webhook update for this component used fallback repository matching "
"instead of an exact repository URL match."
msgstr ""
"ການອັບເດດ webhook ຄັ້ງຫຼ້າສຸດສຳລັບສ່ວນປະກອບນີ້ໄດ້ໃຊ້ວິທີການຈັບຄູ່ຄັງເກັບຂໍ້ມູນແບບສຳຮອງ "
"ແທນທີ່ຈະເປັນການຈັບຄູ່ URL ທີ່ຊັດເຈນ."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/inexacthookmatch.html:8
msgid ""
"This can happen when the component repository URL does not match the "
"repository URL sent by the webhook, or when Weblate does not yet understand "
"the repository URL format in the webhook payload."
msgstr ""
"ສິ່ງນີ້ອາດເກີດຂຶ້ນເມື່ອ URL ຂອງຄັງເກັບຂໍ້ມູນໃນສ່ວນປະກອບບໍ່ກົງກັບ URL ທີ່ສົ່ງມາຈາກ webhook, ຫຼື ເມື່ອ "
"Weblate ຍັງບໍ່ຮອງຮັບຮູບແບບ URL ໃນຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ webhook ສົ່ງມາ."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/inexacthookmatch.html:12
msgid ""
"Check the component repository URL first. If the URL is correct, report the "
"issue to Weblate with the webhook service name, configured component "
"repository URL, branch, and repository URLs from the webhook payload."
msgstr ""
"ກວດສອບ URL ຂອງຄັງເກັບຂໍ້ມູນກ່ອນ. ຖ້າ URL ຖືກຕ້ອງແລ້ວ, ໃຫ້ລາຍງານບັນຫາຕໍ່ Weblate "
"ພ້ອມລະບຸຊື່ບໍລິການ webhook, URL ທີ່ກຳນົດຄ່າໄວ້, ສາຂາ, ແລະ URL ທີ່ໄດ້ຈາກ webhook."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/inexacthookmatch.html:16
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Inexact webhook matching is currently scheduled for removal in Weblate "
"2026.9, see <a href=\"%(issue_url)s\">issue #19855</a>."
msgstr ""
"ການຈັບຄູ່ webhook ແບບບໍ່ຊັດເຈນມີກຳນົດຈະຖືກຍົກເລີກໃນ Weblate 2026.9, ເບິ່ງ <a "
"href=\"%(issue_url)s\">ບັນຫາ #19855</a>."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/inexacthookmatch.html:24
msgid "Service"
msgstr "ບໍລິການ"

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/inexacthookmatch.html:30
msgid "Repository URL"
msgstr "URL ຄັງເກັບຂໍ້ມູນ"

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/inexacthookmatch.html:36
msgid "Repository name"
msgstr "ຊື່ຄັງເກັບຂໍ້ມູນ"

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/inexacthookmatch.html:42
#: weblate/templates/trans/component_create.html:205
#: weblate/templates/vcs/github_installation_detail.html:98
#: weblate/templates/vcs/github_repository_list.html:78
msgid "Branch"
msgstr "ສາຂາ (Branch)"

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/inexacthookmatch.html:52
msgid "Configure component"
msgstr "ກຳນົດຄ່າສ່ວນປະກອບ"

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/inexacthookmatch.html:54
msgid "Report issue"
msgstr "ລາຍງານບັນຫາ"

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/inexistantfiles.html:3
#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/unsupportedconfiguration.html:3
#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/unusedenforcedcheck.html:3
msgid "This component is set up incorrectly."
msgstr "ສ່ວນປະກອບນີ້ຖືກຕັ້ງຄ່າບໍ່ຖືກຕ້ອງ."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/inexistantfiles.html:5
msgid "Following files are no longer present in the repository:"
msgstr "ໄຟລ໌ຕໍ່ໄປນີ້ບໍ່ມີຢູ່ໃນຄັງເກັບຂໍ້ມູນອີກແລ້ວ:"

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/inexistantfiles.html:16
#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:713
msgid "Template for new translations"
msgstr "ແມ່ແບບສຳລັບການແປໃໝ່"

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/mergefailure.html:3
msgid "Weblate could not merge upstream changes while updating the repository."
msgstr "Weblate ບໍ່ສາມາດຮວມ (merge) ການປ່ຽນແປງຈາກຕົ້ນທາງໃນຂະນະທີ່ອັບເດດຄັງເກັບຂໍ້ມູນ."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/missinglicense.html:4
msgid ""
"Any publicly available project should have defined license to indicate what "
"terms apply to contributions."
msgstr ""
"ທຸກໂຄງການທີ່ເປີດເຜີຍຕໍ່ສາທາລະນະຄວນມີການກຳນົດໃບອະນຸຍາດ (license) "
"ເພື່ອບອກເຖິງເງື່ອນໄຂໃນການປະກອບສ່ວນ."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/monolingualglossary.html:4
msgid ""
"Using monolingual files as a glossary is not recommended because adding "
"strings to target language only is not possible in monolingual files."
msgstr ""
"ບໍ່ແນະນຳໃຫ້ໃຊ້ໄຟລ໌ແບບພາສາດຽວເປັນປະມວນສັບ (glossary) ເພາະວ່າທ່ານບໍ່ສາມາດເພີ່ມ "
"ຂໍ້ຄວາມລົງໃນພາສາປາຍທາງໂດຍກົງໄດ້ໃນໄຟລ໌ແບບພາສາດຽວ."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/monolingualglossary.html:7
msgid ""
"You can continue using the glossary this way, but some features will be "
"unavailable."
msgstr "ທ່ານສາມາດສືບຕໍ່ໃຊ້ປະມວນສັບໃນຮູບແບບນີ້ໄດ້, ແຕ່ບາງຟີເຈີຈະບໍ່ສາມາດໃຊ້ງານໄດ້."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/monolingualtranslation.html:3
msgid ""
"The translation component looks monolingual, but it is not set up to be."
msgstr "ສ່ວນປະກອບການແປນີ້ເບິ່ງຄືວ່າເປັນແບບພາສາດຽວ, ແຕ່ຍັງບໍ່ໄດ້ຖືກຕັ້ງຄ່າໃຫ້ເປັນແບບນັ້ນ."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/monolingualtranslation.html:4
msgid "Please add a monolingual base language file in the component settings."
msgstr "ກະລຸນາເພີ່ມໄຟລ໌ພາສາພື້ນຖານແບບພາສາດຽວໃນການຕັ້ງຄ່າສ່ວນປະກອບ."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/nolibreconditions.html:3
msgid "This project does no longer fit into Libre hosting conditions."
msgstr "ໂຄງການນີ້ບໍ່ກົງກັບເງື່ອນໄຂການໂຮສຕິງແບບ Libre ອີກຕໍ່ໄປ."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/nomaskmatches.html:3
msgid "No translations were found for this component file mask."
msgstr "ບໍ່ພົບການແປໃດໆ ສຳລັບຮູບແບບຊື່ໄຟລ໌ (file mask) ຂອງສ່ວນປະກອບນີ້."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/nomaskmatches.html:6
msgid "This is okay when the repository does not contain translations yet."
msgstr "ສິ່ງນີ້ເປັນເລື່ອງປົກກະຕິຖ້າຄັງເກັບຂໍ້ມູນຍັງບໍ່ທັນມີການແປໃດໆ."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/nomaskmatches.html:8
msgid ""
"The alert will disappear once translations are added in Weblate or committed "
"to the repository."
msgstr "ການແຈ້ງເຕືອນນີ້ຈະຫາຍໄປເມື່ອມີການເພີ່ມການແປໃນ Weblate ຫຼື ມີການຄອມມິດລົງໃນຄັງເກັບຂໍ້ມູນ."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/nomaskmatches.html:12
msgid ""
"Starting new translations directly in Weblate is possible, and creates files "
"based on the file mask."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານສາມາດເລີ່ມການແປໃໝ່ໂດຍກົງໃນ Weblate ໄດ້, ແລະ ມັນຈະສ້າງໄຟລ໌ຕາມຮູບແບບຊື່ໄຟລ໌ທີ່ກຳນົດໄວ້."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/nomaskmatches.html:16
#, python-format
msgid ""
"If translations already exist, check whether the file mask "
"<code>%(filemask)s</code> matches files in your version control system "
"repository."
msgstr ""
"ຖ້າມີການແປຢູ່ແລ້ວ, ກະລຸນາກວດສອບວ່າຮູບແບບຊື່ໄຟລ໌ <code>%(filemask)s</code> "
"ກົງກັບໄຟລ໌ໃນຄັງເກັບຂໍ້ມູນຂອງທ່ານ ຫຼື ບໍ່."

#. Translators: This is shown when an alert contains too many occurrences, the count will be always at least 100
#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/occurrences-limit.html:6
#, python-format
msgid "Only some of the %(count)s occurrence is shown."
msgid_plural "Only some of the %(count)s occurrences are shown."
msgstr[0] "ສະແດງພຽງແຕ່ບາງສ່ວນຈາກທັງໝົດ %(count)s ເຫດການ."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/parseerror.html:3
msgid ""
"Weblate could not parse the translation files while updating the "
"translations."
msgstr "Weblate ບໍ່ສາມາດວິເຄາະໄຟລ໌ການແປໄດ້ໃນຂະນະທີ່ອັບເດດການແປ."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/pushfailure.html:3
msgid "Weblate could not push changes to the upstream repository."
msgstr "Weblate ບໍ່ສາມາດສົ່ງ (push) ການປ່ຽນແປງໄປຍັງຄັງເກັບຂໍ້ມູນຕົ້ນທາງໄດ້."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/pushfailure.html:14
msgid "Push the repository"
msgstr "ສົ່ງ (push) ຄັງເກັບຂໍ້ມູນ"

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/repositorychanges.html:4
msgid ""
"The VCS repository has many changes compared to the upstream. Please merge "
"the changes manually or set up push to automate this."
msgstr ""
"ຄັງເກັບຂໍ້ມູນ VCS ມີການປ່ຽນແປງຫຼາຍເມື່ອທຽບກັບຕົ້ນທາງ. ກະລຸນາຮວມການປ່ຽນແປງດ້ວຍຕົນເອງ ຫຼື "
"ຕັ້ງຄ່າການສົ່ງ (push) ອັດຕະໂນມັດ."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/repositoryoperationfailure.html:3
msgid "Weblate could not recover an interrupted repository operation."
msgstr "Weblate ບໍ່ສາມາດກູ້ຄືນການປະຕິບັດງານຂອງຄັງເກັບຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ຖືກຂັດຈັງຫວະໄດ້."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/repositoryoperationfailure.html:14
msgid "Reset the repository"
msgstr "ຕັ້ງຄ່າຄັງເກັບຂໍ້ມູນໃໝ່ (Reset)"

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/repositoryoutdated.html:4
msgid ""
"The VCS repository is not up to date with the upstream one. Please merge "
"changes manually or set up hooks to automate this."
msgstr ""
"ຄັງເກັບຂໍ້ມູນ VCS ບໍ່ເປັນປັດຈຸບັນເມື່ອທຽບກັບຕົ້ນທາງ. ກະລຸນາຮວມການປ່ຽນແປງດ້ວຍຕົນເອງ ຫຼື ຕັ້ງຄ່າ hooks "
"ອັດຕະໂນມັດ."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/unsupportedconfiguration.html:10
#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:580
msgid "Version control system"
msgstr "ແອັບ Weblate GitHub"

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/unsupportedconfiguration.html:23
msgid ""
"This can happen after turning off support for these features, or when "
"dependencies are missing."
msgstr ""
"ສິ່ງນີ້ອາດເກີດຂຶ້ນຫຼັງຈາກປິດການຮອງຮັບຟີເຈີເຫຼົ່ານີ້, ຫຼື ເມື່ອຂາດສ່ວນປະກອບທີ່ຈຳເປັນ (dependencies)."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/unusedcomponent.html:4
#, python-format
msgid "The component has not received any translation within %(count)s day."
msgid_plural ""
"The component has not received any translation within %(count)s days."
msgstr[0] "ສ່ວນປະກອບນີ້ບໍ່ໄດ້ຮັບການແປໃດໆ ເປັນເວລາ %(count)s ມື້ແລ້ວ."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/unusedcomponent.html:7
msgid "Please consider removing the component if it is no longer useful."
msgstr "ກະລຸນາພິຈາລະນາລຶບສ່ວນປະກອບນີ້ອອກ ຖ້າມັນບໍ່ມີປະໂຫຍດອີກຕໍ່ໄປ."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/unusedenforcedcheck.html:5
msgid "Following enforced checks are not used anywhere:"
msgstr "ການກວດສອບທີ່ບັງຄັບຕໍ່ໄປນີ້ບໍ່ໄດ້ຖືກໃຊ້ຢູ່ໃສເລີຍ:"

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/unusedenforcedcheck.html:11
#, python-format
msgid "%(check)s quality check is enforced, but it is not available."
msgstr "ມີການບັງຄັບໃຊ້ການກວດສອບຄຸນນະພາບ %(check)s, ແຕ່ມັນບໍ່ສາມາດໃຊ້ງານໄດ້."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/unusedenforcedcheck.html:15
#, python-format
msgid ""
"%(check)s quality check is enforced, but not turned on using <code>%(flag)s</"
"code> flag."
msgstr ""
"ມີການບັງຄັບໃຊ້ການກວດສອບຄຸນນະພາບ %(check)s, ແຕ່ບໍ່ໄດ້ເປີດໃຊ້ດ້ວຍແຟລັກ (flag) "
"<code>%(flag)s</code>."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/unusedenforcedcheck.html:21
msgid ""
"The check can be turned on by adding the corresponding flag to string or "
"component flags."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານສາມາດເປີດການກວດສອບໄດ້ໂດຍການເພີ່ມແຟລັກ (flag) ທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງເຂົ້າໃນຂໍ້ຄວາມ ຫຼື ສ່ວນປະກອບ."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/unusedglossarylanguage.html:3
msgid ""
"The glossary contains languages not used by any regular component in this "
"project."
msgstr "ປະມວນສັບມີພາສາທີ່ບໍ່ໄດ້ຖືກໃຊ້ໃນສ່ວນປະກອບປົກກະຕິໃດໆ ໃນໂຄງການນີ້."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/unusedglossarylanguage.html:5
msgid ""
"Remove the glossary language if it is no longer needed, or add matching "
"translations to regular components if the glossary should be used."
msgstr ""
"ລຶບພາສາໃນປະມວນສັບອອກຖ້າບໍ່ຈຳເປັນແລ້ວ, ຫຼື ເພີ່ມການແປທີ່ກົງກັນໃນສ່ວນປະກອບປົກກະຕິ "
"ຖ້າຕ້ອງການໃຊ້ປະມວນສັບນັ້ນ."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/unusedscreenshot.html:3
msgid "At least one screenshot has no string assigned to it."
msgstr "ມີຢ່າງໜ້ອຍໜຶ່ງພາບໜ້າຈໍທີ່ບໍ່ມີຂໍ້ຄວາມໃດໆ ຖືກກຳນົດໃຫ້."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/unusedscreenshot.html:6
#: weblate/templates/translate.html:839
