"The new component will be created for the selected branch with the exact "
"same configuration as the existing one."
msgstr "ສ່ວນປະກອບໃໝ່ຈະຖືກສ້າງຂຶ້ນສຳລັບສາຂາທີ່ເລືອກ ໂດຍມີການຕັ້ງຄ່າຄືກັນກັບສ່ວນປະກອບທີ່ມີຢູ່."

#: weblate/templates/trans/component_create.html:138
msgid ""
"Create a new translation component from an uploaded ZIP file containing "
