msgstr "ສ້າງສ່ວນປະກອບການແປໃໝ່ຈາກໄຟລ໌ ZIP ທີ່ອັບໂຫຼດເຊິ່ງມີຂໍ້ຄວາມສຳລັບການແປ."

#: weblate/templates/trans/component_create.html:139
msgid "The filenames within the archive need to have locale codes in them."
msgstr "ຊື່ໄຟລ໌ພາຍໃນໄຟລ໌ ZIP ຕ້ອງມີລະຫັດທ້ອງຖິ່ນ (locale codes) ຢູ່ໃນນັ້ນ."

#: weblate/templates/trans/component_create.html:157
msgid ""
"Create a new translation component from an uploaded document for translation."
msgstr "ສ້າງສ່ວນປະກອບການແປໃໝ່ຈາກເອກະສານທີ່ອັບໂຫຼດເພື່ອການແປ."

#: weblate/templates/trans/component_create.html:174
msgid "Create a new empty translation component to start from scratch."
msgstr "ສ້າງສ່ວນປະກອບການແປໃໝ່ທີ່ຫວ່າງເປົ່າເພື່ອເລີ່ມຈາກສູນ."

#: weblate/templates/trans/component_create.html:175
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Create a ZIP file containing any existing translation files you have, and "
"%(link_start)supload it%(link_end)s."
msgstr ""
"ສ້າງໄຟລ໌ ZIP ທີ່ລວມເອົາໄຟລ໌ການແປທີ່ມີຢູ່ແລ້ວຂອງທ່ານ, ແລ້ວ "
"%(link_start)sອັບໂຫຼດມັນ%(link_end)s."

#: weblate/templates/trans/component_create.html:189
msgid ""
"Pick a repository from a connected account. The component creation form will "
"be pre-filled with the clone URL, default branch, and matching VCS driver."
msgstr ""
"ເລືອກຄັງເກັບຂໍ້ມູນຈາກບັນຊີທີ່ເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ໄວ້. ຟອມສ້າງສ່ວນປະກອບຈະຖືກປ້ອນຂໍ້ມູນ URL ການໂຄລນ, ສາຂາເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ, "
"ແລະ ໄດເວີ VCS ໃຫ້ໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດ."

#: weblate/templates/trans/component_create.html:192
#: weblate/templates/vcs/github_installation_detail.html:23
