#: weblate/templates/trans/merge_instructions.html:5
msgid "Typical workflow for fixing merge conflicts"
msgstr "ຂັ້ນຕອນປົກກະຕິໃນການແກ້ໄຂບັນຫາການຮວມ (merge conflict)"

#: weblate/templates/trans/merge_instructions.html:8
msgid ""
"The exported Weblate repository can be shallow by default, so this workflow "
"works best from an up-to-date upstream checkout. Cloning from the exported "
"Weblate repository or using an outdated upstream checkout can fail even when "
"Weblate and upstream are in sync. See the FAQ below for details."
msgstr ""
"ຄັງເກັບຂໍ້ມູນ Weblate ທີ່ສົ່ງອອກອາດຈະເປັນແບບຕື້ນ (shallow) ໂດຍເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ, "
"ດັ່ງນັ້ນຂັ້ນຕອນນີ້ຈະໄດ້ຜົນດີທີ່ສຸດເມື່ອໃຊ້ກັບຕົ້ນທາງ (upstream) ທີ່ເປັນປັດຈຸບັນ. ການໂຄລນຈາກ Weblate ຫຼື "
"ການໃຊ້ຕົ້ນທາງທີ່ບໍ່ເປັນປັດຈຸບັນອາດຈະຜິດພາດໄດ້. ເບິ່ງລາຍລະອຽດໃນ FAQ."

#: weblate/templates/trans/merge_instructions.html:12
msgid ""
"Open an existing checkout of the upstream repository or perform a fresh one."
msgstr "ເປີດຄັງເກັບຂໍ້ມູນຕົ້ນທາງທີ່ມີຢູ່ ຫຼື ເຮັດການດຶງຂໍ້ມູນໃໝ່."

#: weblate/templates/trans/merge_instructions.html:14
msgid ""
"Commit all pending changes in Weblate and lock the translation component."
msgstr "ຄອມມິດການປ່ຽນແປງທີ່ຄ້າງຢູ່ທັງໝົດໃນ Weblate ແລະ ລັອກສ່ວນປະກອບການແປ."

#: weblate/templates/trans/merge_instructions.html:19
msgid "Add Weblate exported repository as a remote."
msgstr "ເພີ່ມຄັງເກັບຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ສົ່ງອອກຈາກ Weblate ເປັນ remote."

#: weblate/templates/trans/merge_instructions.html:24
msgid "Merge Weblate changes and resolve any conflicts."
msgstr "ຮວມ (merge) ການປ່ຽນແປງຈາກ Weblate ແລະ ແກ້ໄຂຂໍ້ຂັດແຍ່ງ (conflicts)."

#: weblate/templates/trans/merge_instructions.html:30
msgid "Rebase Weblate changes on top of upstream and resolve any conflicts."
msgstr "Rebase ການປ່ຽນແປງຈາກ Weblate ລົງເທິງຕົ້ນທາງ ແລະ ແກ້ໄຂຂໍ້ຂັດແຍ່ງ."

#: weblate/templates/trans/merge_instructions.html:36
msgid "Push changes into upstream repository."
msgstr "ສົ່ງ (push) ການປ່ຽນແປງໄປຍັງຄັງເກັບຂໍ້ມູນຕົ້ນທາງ."

#: weblate/templates/trans/merge_instructions.html:41
msgid ""
"Weblate should now be able to see updated repository and you can unlock it."
msgstr "ດຽວນີ້ Weblate ຄວນຈະເຫັນຄັງເກັບຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ອັບເດດແລ້ວ ແລະ ທ່ານສາມາດປົດລັອກມັນໄດ້."

#: weblate/templates/trans/merge_instructions.html:50
