msgstr "ລະຫັດຕົວອັກສອນທີ່ໃຊ້ສຳລັບໄຟລ໌ Java Properties"

#: weblate/trans/file_format_params.py:634
#: weblate/trans/file_format_params.py:648
msgid "Auto-detect"
msgstr "ກວດຫາອັດຕະໂນມັດ"

#: weblate/trans/file_format_params.py:638
msgid "Encoding used for CSV files"
msgstr "ລະຫັດຕົວອັກສອນທີ່ໃຊ້ສຳລັບໄຟລ໌ CSV"

#: weblate/trans/file_format_params.py:653
msgid "Encoding used for simple CSV files"
msgstr "ລະຫັດຕົວອັກສອນທີ່ໃຊ້ສຳລັບໄຟລ໌ CSV ແບບງ່າຍ"

#: weblate/trans/file_format_params.py:660
msgid "Escape spreadsheet formulas"
msgstr "Escape ສູດຕາຕະລາງ (Spreadsheet formulas)"

#: weblate/trans/file_format_params.py:664
msgid ""
"Prefix values that look like spreadsheet formulas with an apostrophe when "
"saving CSV files."
msgstr "ໃສ່ເຄື່ອງໝາຍຝົນທອງ (Apostrophe) ນຳໜ້າຄ່າທີ່ເບິ່ງຄືສູດຕາຕະລາງເມື່ອບັນທຶກໄຟລ໌ CSV."

#: weblate/trans/file_format_params.py:685
msgid "Encoding used for GWT Properties files"
msgstr "ລະຫັດຕົວອັກສອນທີ່ໃຊ້ສຳລັບໄຟລ໌ GWT Properties"

#: weblate/trans/file_format_params.py:692
msgid "DOS line endings"
msgstr "ການຈົບແຖວແບບ DOS"

#: weblate/trans/file_format_params.py:696
msgid ""
"Use DOS line endings (\\r\\n) instead of UNIX line endings (\\n) in strings."
msgstr "ໃຊ້ການຈົບແຖວແບບ DOS (\\r\\n) ແທນທີ່ UNIX (\\n) ໃນຂໍ້ຄວາມ."

#: weblate/trans/file_format_params.py:704
msgid "Maximum line length"
msgstr "ຄວາມຍາວແຖວສູງສຸດ"

#: weblate/trans/file_format_params.py:709
msgid "The maximum number of characters for each line in the output file."
msgstr "ຈຳນວນຕົວອັກສອນສູງສຸດສຳລັບແຕ່ລະແຖວໃນໄຟລ໌ຜົນລັດ."

#: weblate/trans/file_format_params.py:717
msgid "Extract code blocks"
msgstr "ດຶງຂໍ້ມູນບລັອກໂຄດ"

#: weblate/trans/file_format_params.py:721
msgid ""
"Whether to extract translatable content from code blocks in Markdown and MDX "
"files."
msgstr "ກຳນົດວ່າຈະດຶງເນື້ອຫາທີ່ແປໄດ້ຈາກບລັອກໂຄດໃນໄຟລ໌ Markdown ແລະ MDX ຫຼື ບໍ່."

#: weblate/trans/file_format_params.py:729
msgid "Extract front matter"
msgstr "ດຶງຂໍ້ມູນ Front matter"

#: weblate/trans/file_format_params.py:733
msgid ""
"Whether to extract and translate YAML front matter blocks in Markdown and "
"MDX files."
msgstr "ກຳນົດວ່າຈະດຶງ ແລະ ແປບລັອກ YAML front matter ໃນໄຟລ໌ Markdown ແລະ MDX ຫຼື ບໍ່."

#: weblate/trans/file_format_params.py:741
msgid "Translate front matter values"
msgstr "ແປຄ່າໃນ Front matter"

#: weblate/trans/file_format_params.py:745
msgid ""
"Parse YAML front matter and translate only scalar string values. Keys, "
"structure, comments, and formatting are preserved when possible."
msgstr ""
"ວິເຄາະ YAML front matter ແລະ ແປສະເພາະຄ່າຂໍ້ຄວາມ. ສ່ວນ Keys, ໂຄງສ້າງ, ຄຳເຫັນ ແລະ "
"ຮູບແບບຈະຖືກຮັກສາໄວ້."

#: weblate/trans/file_format_params.py:754
msgid "Disable placeholders"
msgstr "ປິດໃຊ້ງານ Placeholder"

#: weblate/trans/file_format_params.py:758
msgid ""
"Disables detection and processing of placeholders in Markdown and MDX files."
msgstr "ປິດການກວດຫາ ແລະ ການປະມວນຜົນ Placeholder ໃນໄຟລ໌ Markdown ແລະ MDX."

