msgid ""
"This field is managed by the repository integration and can not be changed."
msgstr "ຟິນນີ້ຖືກຈັດການໂດຍການເຊື່ອມໂຍງຄັງເກັບ ແລະ ບໍ່ສາມາດປ່ຽນແປງໄດ້."

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:583
msgid ""
"Version control system to use to access your repository containing "
"translations. You can also choose additional integration with third party "
"providers to submit pull/merge requests."
msgstr ""
"ລະບົບຄວບຄຸມເວີຊັນທີ່ຈະໃຊ້ເພື່ອເຂົ້າເຖິງຄັງເກັບຂອງທ່ານທີ່ມີການແປ. "
"ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດເລືອກການເຊື່ອມໂຍງເພີ່ມເຕີມກັບຜູ້ໃຫ້ບໍລິການພາຍນອກເພື່ອສົ່ງ pull/merge requests."

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:595
msgid ""
"URL of a repository, use weblate://project/component to share it with other "
"component."
msgstr "URL ຂອງຄັງເກັບ, ໃຊ້ weblate://project/component ເພື່ອແບ່ງປັນກັບສ່ວນປະກອບອື່ນ."

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:608
msgid "Repository push URL"
msgstr "URL ສຳລັບ push ຄັງເກັບ"

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:611
msgid ""
"URL of a push repository, pushing is turned off if empty. When using pull/"
"merge requests, keep empty to fork the repository."
msgstr ""
"URL ຂອງຄັງເກັບສຳລັບ push, ການ push ຈະຖືກປິດຫາກວ່າງເປົ່າ. ເມື່ອໃຊ້ pull/merge requests, "
"ໃຫ້ປະຫວ່າງໄວ້ເພື່ອ fork ຄັງເກັບ."

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:617
msgid "Repository browser"
msgstr "ຕົວເບິ່ງຄັງເກັບ"

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:620
msgid ""
"Link to repository browser, use {{branch}} for branch, {{filename}} and "
"{{line}} as filename and line placeholders. You might want to strip leading "
"directory by using {{filename|parentdir}}."
msgstr ""
"ລິ້ງໄປຫາຕົວເບິ່ງຄັງເກັບ, ໃຊ້ {{branch}} ສຳລັບສາຂາ, {{filename}} ແລະ {{line}} "
"ເປັນບ່ອນວາງຊື່ໄຟລ໌ ແລະ ແຖວ. ທ່ານອາດຈະຕ້ອງການຕັດໂຟນເດີເລີ່ມຕົ້ນອອກໂດຍໃຊ້ {{filename|"
"parentdir}}."

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:628
msgid "Exported repository URL"
msgstr "URL ຄັງເກັບທີ່ສົ່ງອອກ"

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:631
msgid "URL of repository where users can fetch changes from Weblate"
msgstr "URL ຂອງຄັງເກັບທີ່ຜູ້ໃຊ້ສາມາດດຶງການປ່ຽນແປງຈາກ Weblate"

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:636
msgid "Source string bug reporting address"
msgstr "ທີ່ຢູ່ລາຍງານຂໍ້ຜິດພາດຂອງຂໍ້ຄວາມຕົ້ນສະບັບ"

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:638
msgid ""
"E-mail address for reports on errors in source strings. Leave empty for no e-"
"mails."
msgstr "ທີ່ຢູ່ອີເມວສຳລັບລາຍງານຂໍ້ຜິດພາດໃນຂໍ້ຄວາມຕົ້ນສະບັບ. ປະຫວ່າງໄວ້ຫາກບໍ່ຕ້ອງການອີເມວ."

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:646
msgid "Repository branch to translate"
msgstr "ສາຂາຄັງເກັບທີ່ຈະແປ"

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:651
msgid "Push branch"
msgstr "ສາຂາທີ່ຈະ push"

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:654
msgid ""
"Branch for pushing changes. Leave empty to use repository branch when "
"pushing directly to the repository. When using pull/merge requests, specify "
"a branch name different from the repository branch."
msgstr ""
"ສາຂາສຳລັບ push ການປ່ຽນແປງ. ປະຫວ່າງໄວ້ເພື່ອໃຊ້ສາຂາຄັງເກັບເມື່ອ push ໂດຍກົງຫາຄັງເກັບ. ເມື່ອໃຊ້ "
"pull/merge requests, ໃຫ້ລະບຸຊື່ສາຂາທີ່ແຕກຕ່າງຈາກສາຂາຄັງເກັບ."

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:666
msgid ""
"Path of files to translate relative to repository root, use * instead of "
"language code, for example: po/*.po or locale/*/LC_MESSAGES/django.po."
msgstr ""
"ເສັ້ນທາງຂອງໄຟລ໌ທີ່ຈະແປທຽບກັບຮາກຂອງຄັງເກັບ, ໃຊ້ * ແທນລະຫັດພາສາ, ຕົວຢ່າງ: po/*.po ຫຼື locale/"
"*/LC_MESSAGES/django.po."

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:672
msgid "Screenshot file mask"
msgstr "ໜ້າກາກໄຟລ໌ພາບໜ້າຈໍ"

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:677
msgid ""
"Path of screenshots relative to repository root, for example: docs/"
"screenshots/*.png."
msgstr "ເສັ້ນທາງຂອງພາບໜ້າຈໍທຽບກັບຮາກຂອງຄັງເກັບ, ຕົວຢ່າງ: docs/screenshots/*.png."

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:686
msgid ""
"Filename of translation base file, containing all strings and their source "
"for monolingual translations."
msgstr ""
"ຊື່ໄຟລ໌ຂອງໄຟລ໌ພື້ນຖານການແປ, ເຊິ່ງປະກອບດ້ວຍຂໍ້ຄວາມທັງໝົດ ແລະ "
"ຕົ້ນສະບັບສຳລັບການແປແບບພາສາພຽງຢ່າງດຽວ (Monolingual)."

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:693
msgid "Edit base file"
msgstr "ແກ້ໄຂໄຟລ໌ພື້ນຖານ"

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:696
msgid ""
"Whether users will be able to edit the base file for monolingual "
"translations."
msgstr "ຜູ້ໃຊ້ຈະສາມາດແກ້ໄຂໄຟລ໌ພື້ນຖານສຳລັບການແປແບບພາສາພຽງຢ່າງດຽວໄດ້ຫຼືບໍ່."

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:705
msgid ""
"Filename of intermediate translation file. In most cases this is a "
"translation file provided by developers and is used when creating actual "
"source strings."
msgstr ""
"ຊື່ໄຟລ໌ຂອງໄຟລ໌ການແປລະຫວ່າງກາງ. ສ່ວນຫຼາຍແມ່ນໄຟລ໌ການແປທີ່ນັກພັດທະນາສະໜອງໃຫ້ ແລະ "
"ຖືກໃຊ້ເມື່ອສ້າງຂໍ້ຄວາມຕົ້ນສະບັບຕົວຈິງ."

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:717
msgid ""
"Filename of file used for creating new translations. For gettext choose .pot "
"file."
msgstr "ຊື່ໄຟລ໌ຂອງໄຟລ໌ທີ່ໃຊ້ສຳລັບສ້າງການແປໃໝ່. ສຳລັບ gettext ໃຫ້ເລືອກໄຟລ໌ .pot."

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:730
msgid "File format parameters"
msgstr "ພາລາມິເຕີຮູບແບບໄຟລ໌"

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:740
msgid "Locked component will not get any translation updates."
msgstr "ສ່ວນປະກອບທີ່ຖືກລັອກຈະບໍ່ໄດ້ຮັບການອັບເດດການແປໃດໆ."

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:744
msgid "Do not show glossary matches"
msgstr "ບໍ່ຕ້ອງສະແດງຄຳສັບທີ່ກົງກັບອະພິທານສັບ"

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:746
msgid "Hides the glossary panel in the translation editor."
msgstr "ເຊື່ອງແຖບອະພິທານສັບໃນຕົວແກ້ໄຂການແປ."

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:749
msgid "Allow translation propagation"
msgstr "ອະນຸຍາດການກະຈາຍການແປ"

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:752
msgid ""
"Whether translation updates in other components will cause automatic "
"translation in this one"
msgstr "ການອັບເດດການແປໃນສ່ວນປະກອບອື່ນໆຈະເຮັດໃຫ້ເກີດການແປອັດຕະໂນມັດໃນສ່ວນປະກອບນີ້ຫຼືບໍ່"

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:757
msgid "Contribute to project translation memory"
msgstr "ປະກອບສ່ວນເຂົ້າໃນຄວາມຈຳການແປ (Translation memory) ຂອງໂຄງການ"

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:760
msgid ""
"Allow this component's translations to be added to the project-level "
"translation memory."
msgstr "ອະນຸຍາດໃຫ້ການແປຂອງສ່ວນປະກອບນີ້ຖືກເພີ່ມເຂົ້າໃນຄວາມຈຳການແປລະດັບໂຄງການ."

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:766 weblate/trans/models/workflow.py:30
msgid "Turn on suggestions"
msgstr "ເປີດໃຊ້ການແນະນຳ"

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:768 weblate/trans/models/workflow.py:32
msgid "Whether to allow translation suggestions at all."
msgstr "ຈະອະນຸຍາດໃຫ້ມີການແນະນຳການແປຫຼືບໍ່."

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:772 weblate/trans/models/workflow.py:36
msgid "Suggestion voting"
msgstr "ການລົງຄະແນນສຽງການແນະນຳ"

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:775 weblate/trans/models/workflow.py:39
msgid "Users can only vote for suggestions and can’t make direct translations."
msgstr "ຜູ້ໃຊ້ສາມາດລົງຄະແນນສຽງໃຫ້ກັບການແນະນຳເທົ່ານັ້ນ ແລະ ບໍ່ສາມາດແປໂດຍກົງໄດ້."

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:780 weblate/trans/models/workflow.py:44
msgid "Automatically accept suggestions"
msgstr "ຍອມຮັບການແນະນຳໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດ"

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:783 weblate/trans/models/workflow.py:47
msgid ""
"Automatically accept suggestions with this number of votes, use 0 to turn it "
"off."
msgstr "ຍອມຮັບການແນະນຳໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດເມື່ອມີຄະແນນສຽງເຖິງຈຳນວນນີ້, ໃຊ້ 0 ເພື່ອປິດການໃຊ້ງານ."

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:798
msgid "Enforced checks"
msgstr "ການກວດສອບທີ່ບັງຄັບ"

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:799
msgid "List of checks which can not be dismissed."
msgstr "ລາຍການການກວດສອບທີ່ບໍ່ສາມາດຍົກເລີກໄດ້."

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:816
msgid "Use the translation license configured in the category or project."
msgstr "ໃຊ້ໃບອະນຸຍາດການແປທີ່ກຳນົດໄວ້ໃນໝວດໝູ່ ຫຼື ໂຄງການ."

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:824
msgid ""
"Contributor license agreement which needs to be approved before a user can "
"translate this component."
msgstr "ຂໍ້ຕົກລົງອະນຸຍາດຜູ້ປະກອບສ່ວນເຊິ່ງຕ້ອງໄດ້ຮັບການອະນຸມັດກ່ອນທີ່ຜູ້ໃຊ້ຈະສາມາດແປສ່ວນປະກອບນີ້ໄດ້."

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:832
msgid ""
"Use the contributor license agreement configured in the category or project."
msgstr "ໃຊ້ຂໍ້ຕົກລົງອະນຸຍາດຜູ້ປະກອບສ່ວນທີ່ກຳນົດໄວ້ໃນໝວດໝູ່ ຫຼື ໂຄງການ."

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:848
msgid ""
"Use the adding new translations setting configured in the category or "
"project."
msgstr "ໃຊ້ການຕັ້ງຄ່າການເພີ່ມການແປໃໝ່ທີ່ກຳນົດໄວ້ໃນໝວດໝູ່ ຫຼື ໂຄງການ."

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:866
msgid "Use the language code style configured in the category or project."
msgstr "ໃຊ້ຮູບແບບລະຫັດພາສາທີ່ກຳນົດໄວ້ໃນໝວດໝູ່ ຫຼື ໂຄງການ."

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:870
msgid "Manage strings"
msgstr "ຈັດການຂໍ້ຄວາມ"

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:873
msgid ""
"Enables adding and removing strings straight from Weblate. If your strings "
"are extracted from the source code or managed externally you probably want "
"to keep it disabled."
msgstr ""
"ເປີດໃຊ້ການເພີ່ມ ແລະ ລຶບຂໍ້ຄວາມໂດຍກົງຈາກ Weblate. ຫາກຂໍ້ຄວາມຂອງທ່ານຖືກສະກັດຈາກຊອດໂຄ້ດ ຫຼື "
"ຈັດການຈາກພາຍນອກ ທ່ານອາດຈະຕ້ອງການປິດອັນນີ້ໄວ້."

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:881
msgid "Merge style"
msgstr "ຮູບແບບການລວມ (Merge style)"

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:886
msgid ""
"Define whether Weblate should merge the upstream repository or rebase "
"changes onto it."
msgstr "ກຳນົດວ່າ Weblate ຄວນລວມຄັງເກັບຕົ້ນທາງ (Merge) ຫຼື Rebase ການປ່ຽນແປງໃສ່ມັນ."

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:903
msgid ""
"Use the commit message when translating configured in the category or "
"project."
msgstr "ໃຊ້ຂໍ້ຄວາມບັນທຶກການປ່ຽນແປງເມື່ອແປທີ່ກຳນົດໄວ້ໃນໝວດໝູ່ ຫຼື ໂຄງການ."

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:919
msgid ""
"Use the commit message when adding translation configured in the category or "
"project."
msgstr "ໃຊ້ຂໍ້ຄວາມບັນທຶກການປ່ຽນແປງເມື່ອເພີ່ມການແປທີ່ກຳນົດໄວ້ໃນໝວດໝູ່ ຫຼື ໂຄງການ."

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:935
msgid ""
"Use the commit message when removing translation configured in the category "
"or project."
msgstr "ໃຊ້ຂໍ້ຄວາມບັນທຶກການປ່ຽນແປງເມື່ອລຶບການແປທີ່ກຳນົດໄວ້ໃນໝວດໝູ່ ຫຼື ໂຄງການ."

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:952
msgid ""
"Use the commit message when merging translation configured in the category "
"or project."
msgstr "ໃຊ້ຂໍ້ຄວາມບັນທຶກການປ່ຽນແປງເມື່ອລວມການແປທີ່ກຳນົດໄວ້ໃນໝວດໝູ່ ຫຼື ໂຄງການ."

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:968
msgid ""
"Use the commit message when add-on makes a change configured in the category "
"or project."
msgstr "ໃຊ້ຂໍ້ຄວາມບັນທຶກການປ່ຽນແປງເມື່ອສ່ວນເສີມເຮັດການປ່ຽນແປງທີ່ກຳນົດໄວ້ໃນໝວດໝູ່ ຫຼື ໂຄງການ."

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:984
msgid "Use the merge request message configured in the category or project."
msgstr "ໃຊ້ຂໍ້ຄວາມຄຳຮ້ອງຂໍລວມທີ່ກຳນົດໄວ້ໃນໝວດໝູ່ ຫຼື ໂຄງການ."

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:988
msgid "Push on commit"
msgstr "Push ເມື່ອບັນທຶກການປ່ຽນແປງ (Commit)"

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:991
msgid "Whether the repository should be pushed upstream on every commit."
msgstr "ຄວນ push ຄັງເກັບໄປຍັງຕົ້ນທາງໃນທຸກໆການ commit ຫຼື ບໍ່."

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:995
msgid "Age of changes to commit"
msgstr "ອາຍຸຂອງການປ່ຽນແປງທີ່ຈະ commit"

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:999
msgid ""
"Time in hours after which any pending changes will be committed to the VCS."
msgstr "ເວລາເປັນຊົ່ວໂມງທີ່ການປ່ຽນແປງທີ່ຄ້າງຢູ່ຈະຖືກ commit ໄປຍັງ VCS."

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:1004
