msgstr "ລັອກເມື່ອເກີດຂໍ້ຜິດພາດ"

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:1007
msgid "Whether the component should be locked on repository errors."
msgstr "ສ່ວນປະກອບຄວນຖືກລັອກເມື່ອເກີດຂໍ້ຜິດພາດຂອງຄັງເກັບຫຼືບໍ່."

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:1014
msgid "Language used for source strings in all components"
msgstr "ພາສາທີ່ໃຊ້ສຳລັບຂໍ້ຄວາມຕົ້ນສະບັບໃນທຸກສ່ວນປະກອບ"

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:1024
msgid ""
"Regular expression used to filter translation files when scanning for file "
