msgstr "ນິພົດປົກກະຕິ (Regular expression) ທີ່ໃຊ້ເພື່ອຫາໄຟລ໌ການແປເມື່ອສະແກນຫາໜ້າກາກໄຟລ໌."

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:1029
msgid "Variants regular expression"
msgstr "ນິພົດປົກກະຕິຂອງລຸ້ນຍ່ອຍ (Variants)"

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:1035
msgid "Regular expression used to determine variants of a string."
msgstr "ນິພົດປົກກະຕິທີ່ໃຊ້ເພື່ອລະບຸລຸ້ນຍ່ອຍຂອງຂໍ້ຄວາມ."

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:1044
msgid "Components with higher priority are offered first to translators."
msgstr "ສ່ວນປະກອບທີ່ມີລຳດັບຄວາມສຳຄັນສູງກວ່າຈະຖືກສະເໜີໃຫ້ຜູ້ແປກ່ອນ."

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:1048
#: weblate/trans/templatetags/translations.py:1244
msgid "Restricted component"
msgstr "ສ່ວນປະກອບທີ່ຖືກຈຳກັດ"

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:1052
msgid ""
"Restrict access to the component to only those explicitly given permission."
msgstr "ຈຳກັດການເຂົ້າເຖິງສ່ວນປະກອບສະເພາະຜູ້ທີ່ໄດ້ຮັບອະນຸຍາດຢ່າງຊັດເຈນເທົ່ານັ້ນ."

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:1064
msgid "Choose additional projects where this component will be listed."
msgstr "ເລືອກໂຄງການເພີ່ມເຕີມທີ່ຈະສະແດງສ່ວນປະກອບນີ້."

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:1070
msgid "Use as a glossary"
msgstr "ໃຊ້ເປັນອະພິທານສັບ"

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:1074
msgid ""
"Glossaries are different from regular translations but help keep track of "
"and share consistent terminology."
msgstr "ອະພິທານສັບແຕກຕ່າງຈາກການແປທົ່ວໄປ ແຕ່ຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ຕິດຕາມ ແລະ ແບ່ງປັນຄຳສັບທີ່ສອດຄ່ອງກັນ."

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:1078
msgid "Glossary color"
msgstr "ສີອະພິທານສັບ"

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:1089
msgid "Key filter"
msgstr "ຕົວກັ່ນຕອງຄີ"

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:1093
msgid ""
"Regular expression used to filter keys. This is only available for "
"monolingual formats."
msgstr "ນິພົດປົກກະຕິທີ່ໃຊ້ເພື່ອການກັ່ນຕອງຄີ. ອັນນີ້ມີໃຫ້ສະເພາະຮູບແບບພາສາພຽງຢ່າງດຽວເທົ່ານັ້ນ."

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:1106
msgid "This setting is inherited from the project if left empty."
msgstr "ການຕັ້ງຄ່ານີ້ຈະຖືກສືບທອດມາຈາກໂຄງການຫາກປະຫວ່າງໄວ້."

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:1118
msgid "Use the secondary language configured in the category or project."
msgstr "ໃຊ້ພາສາທີສອງທີ່ກຳນົດໄວ້ໃນໝວດໝູ່ ຫຼື ໂຄງການ."

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:2421
msgid ""
"Could not verify the SSH host key. Please add it on the SSH page in the "
"admin interface."
msgstr "ບໍ່ສາມາດຢືນຢັນຄີ SSH host ໄດ້. ກະລຸນາເພີ່ມມັນຢູ່ໃນໜ້າ SSH ໃນສ່ວນຜູ້ດູແລ."

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:2427
msgid ""
"The SSH host key for the repository has changed. Verify the new fingerprint, "
"remove the stored host key, and add the new one on the SSH page in the admin "
"interface."
msgstr ""
"ຄີ SSH host ສຳລັບຄັງເກັບມີການປ່ຽນແປງ. ກະລຸນາຢືນຢັນລາຍນິ້ວມືໃໝ່, ລຶບຄີ host ທີ່ເກັບໄວ້, ແລະ "
"ເເພີ່ມຄີໃໝ່ໃນໜ້າ SSH ໃນສ່ວນຜູ້ດູແລ."

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:2464
msgid ""
"The repository requires authentication, please specify credentials in the "
"URL or use SSH access instead."
msgstr ""
"ຄັງເກັບຕ້ອງການການຢືນຢັນຕົວຕົນ, ກະລຸນາລະບຸຂໍ້ມູນປະຈຳຕົວໃນ URL ຫຼື ໃຊ້ການເຂົ້າເຖິງຜ່ານ SSH ແທນ."

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:2470
#, python-format
