#: weblate/trans/models/project.py:299
msgid ""
"Contributes translations to the pool shared between projects in the "
"workspace."
msgstr "ປະກອບສ່ວນການແປເຂົ້າໃນກຸ່ມທີ່ແບ່ງປັນກັນລະຫວ່າງໂຄງການຕ່າງໆໃນພື້ນທີ່ເຮັດວຽກ."

#: weblate/trans/models/project.py:306
msgid ""
"Automatically removes outdated and obsolete entries from translation memory."
msgstr "ລຶບລາຍການທີ່ຫຼ້າສະໄໝ ແລະ ບໍ່ໄດ້ໃຊ້ແລ້ວອອກຈາກຄວາມຈຳການແປໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດ."

#: weblate/trans/models/project.py:315
msgid ""
"How to restrict access to this project is detailed in the documentation."
msgstr "ວິທີການຈຳກັດການເຂົ້າເຖິງໂຄງການນີ້ມີລາຍລະອຽດຢູ່ໃນເອກະສານຄູ່ມື."

#: weblate/trans/models/project.py:323
msgid ""
"Requires contributors to have two-factor authentication configured before "
"being able to contribute."
msgstr "ກຳນົດໃຫ້ຜູ້ປະກອບສ່ວນຕ້ອງຕັ້ງຄ່າການຢືນຢັນຕົວຕົນສອງຂັ້ນຕອນກ່ອນຈຶ່ງຈະສາມາດປະກອບສ່ວນໄດ້."

#: weblate/trans/models/project.py:328 weblate/trans/models/workflow.py:24
msgid "Enable reviews"
msgstr "ເປີດໃຊ້ການກວດສອບ (Reviews)"

#: weblate/trans/models/project.py:330 weblate/trans/models/workflow.py:26
msgid "Requires dedicated reviewers to approve translations."
msgstr "ກຳນົດໃຫ້ມີຜູ້ກວດສອບສະເພາະເພື່ອອະນຸມັດການແປ."

#: weblate/trans/models/project.py:333
msgid "Enable source reviews"
msgstr "ເປີດໃຊ້ການກວດສອບຕົ້ນສະບັບ"

#: weblate/trans/models/project.py:336
msgid "Requires dedicated reviewers to approve source strings."
msgstr "ກຳນົດໃຫ້ມີຜູ້ກວດສອບສະເພາະເພື່ອອະນຸມັດຂໍ້ຄວາມຕົ້ນສະບັບ."

#: weblate/trans/models/project.py:344
msgid ""
"Select which translations should be included when committing changes. More "
"restrictive options will skip translations with potential quality issues."
msgstr ""
"ເລືອກການແປທີ່ຈະລວມເຂົ້າເມື່ອ commit ການປ່ຽນແປງ. "
"ຕົວເລືອກທີ່ເຂັ້ມງວດກວ່າຈະຂ້າມການແປທີ່ມີບັນຫາດ້ານຄຸນນະພາບ."

#: weblate/trans/models/project.py:349
msgid "Enable hooks"
msgstr "ເປີດໃຊ້ Hooks"

#: weblate/trans/models/project.py:352
msgid "Whether to allow updating this repository by remote hooks."
msgstr "ອະນຸຍາດໃຫ້ອັບເດດຄັງເກັບນີ້ໂດຍ remote hooks ຫຼື ບໍ່."

#: weblate/trans/models/project.py:356
msgid "Language aliases"
msgstr "ນາມແຝງພາສາ"

#: weblate/trans/models/project.py:360
msgid ""
